SEILA LAW LLC, Petitioner,
v.
CONSUMER FINANCIAL PROTECTION BUREAU. No. 19-7. Supreme Court of the United States. Oct. 23, 2019. Paul D. Clement, Esquire, of Washington, D. C., is invited to brief and argue this case, as amicus curie, in support of the judgment below on the question presented by the petition.
